Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a monitoring system using a deep learning model to identify license plates of vehicles in an underground garage. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper proposes the use of a self-driving mini-car to implement the monitoring system. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another likely category as the paper proposes the use of a deep learning model for license plate recognition. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a possible category as the paper proposes the use of a deep learning model for license plate recognition. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper addresses security concerns related to apartment garages and proposes a solution to keep tenants' goods safe.
